{"tid":2231663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛: 調查新冠病毒源頭的國際專家名單須先提交給中國審核","createTime":"2020-10-05T23:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T14:01:56.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":298,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ead68046dfdbc8a4c62a30f4ac771bf4638a38","tid":2231663,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際要求對2019冠狀病毒疾病源頭赴中國展開實地調查，世界衛生組織官員今天證實，<strong><span class=\"red\">國際代表團的專家名單須先提供給中國</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n據中央社今天報道稱，世界衛生組織（WHO）執行委員會今天起一連2天召開2019冠狀病毒疾病應對特別會議，世衛公共衛生緊急計畫執行主任萊恩（Michael Ryan）在疫情流行病學分析時表示，世衛將組成一個國際專家團前往中國，以調查病毒起源，且已經提交專家名單給中國當局考慮（consideration）。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201005-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=7caa469a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"81b68279ecf7e54fde3693a64dbed24a8468ab02","tid":2231663,"uid":234089,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:05:48.000Z","msg":"留名全部自己人"},{"pid":"28f2c193f2e27fde2427577dae7a4e76b9a4a293","tid":2231663,"uid":204533,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"quote":{"pid":"81b68279ecf7e54fde